/                                                               /__  \
|   _       _____                                               |(_\ /
|  | |     / ____|                                              \-`-'
|  | |    | (___                                                |
|  | |     \___ \                                               |
|  | |____ ____) |                                              |
|  |______|_____/                                               |
|                                                               |
|                                                               |
|  This spell shows you your surroundings.                      |
|                                                               |
|                                                               |
|  Examples                                                     |
|                                                               |
|  ls                                                           |
|  Shows you what is around your current position               |
|                                                               |
|  ls kitchen                                                   |
|  Shows you what is in the directory kitchen,                  |
|  assuming you are in my-house                                 |
|                                                               |
|  ls ../                                                       |
|  Shows you what is in the directory behind you                |
|                                                               |
|  ls ~/my-house/kitchen                                        |
|  Regardless of your current position, this will               |
|  show you what is in your kitchen                             |
|                                                               |
|  Flags                                                        |
|                                                               |
|  -a                                                           |
|  This shows all the files in your current directory,          |
|  including the hidden files starting with .                   |
|  This includes your current position . and the                |
|  containing directory ..                                      |
|                                                               |
|  Example                                                      |
|                                                               |
|  ls -a ../                                                    |
|  Will show you everything in the directory behind you         |____
|                                                               |__( \
\                                                               \    /
 `---------------------------------------------------------------`=='
